In a skillet, saute onion in butter. Remove from the heat; stir in spinach, salt and nutmeg. In a bowl, combine cottage cheese, cream, Parmesan cheese and eggs; mix well. Stir in spinach mixture. Pour into pie shell. Bake at 350 degrees F for 45-50 minutes, or until a knife inserted near the center comes out clean. Let stand for 5 minutes before cutting.